1. Start
2. Display Welcome Message
3. Repeat until user chooses to exit:
    a. Display MENU: Addition, Subtraction, Multiplication, Division, or Exit
    b. Get user choice
    c. If user choice is Exit, display Exit message and end
    d. If user choice is a valid operation:
        i. Display chosen operation
        ii. Input two numbers
        iii. If input is valid:
            A. Perform the selected operation
            B. Display the result
        iv. If input is not valid, display an error message
4. End
